rich_message.text: Isang mapagpalang araw, FEU Institute of Education Students!
Our Directorship and Exe-Com Membership Applications for the IE Student Council 2025–2026 are still OPEN until tomorrow at 12NN!
Kung sa k-drama may second lead, dito sa IE Council, ikaw ang bida!  Don’t miss the chance to lead, serve, and unlock your full potential (plus, may bragging rights ka na “Council ako dati” 😎).
It’s our time na, TamEdukista’s! 🙌

Departments Open (a.k.a. your future tambayan 😏):

1. Office of the President (OPres)
Student Welfare and Grievances Response Dept. (para sa mga marites ng complaints—pero in a good way)

Sports and Talents Dept. (kung kaya mong mag-cheer kahit walang boses, this is for you)

2. Office of the Vice President (OVP)
Legal and Legislative Dept. (seryoso pero hindi boring, promise)

Sponsorship and Partnership Dept. (the more, the merrier, and the sponsored)

3. Office of the Secretary (OSec)

Narrative and Archives Dept. (aka “official historian” — ikaw na magpapaalala kung sino ang late kahapon)

4. Office of the Treasurer (OTreas)
Logistics and Purchasing Dept. (kayang magdala ng 10 reams of bond paper nang sabay-sabay)

Finance and Accounting Dept. (kung favorite subject mo “utang”, bagay ka dito)

5. Office of the Auditor (OAudit)
Audit Dept. (para sa mga mahilig magbilang kahit butil ng bigas)

Internal and Disciplinary Dept. (tagabantay ng curfew, kahit wala tayong curfew)

6. Office of the Public Relations Officer (OPRO)
External & Strategic Communication Dept. (para sa mga future chismologist pero classy)
Events Dept. (kayo ang reason kung bakit may pa-Zumba si sir/ma’am)
Multimedia & Creatives Dept. (a.k.a. “poster is life” gang)
So, ano pa hinihintay niyo? Apply na! Kahit wala kang cape, pwede kang maging hero ng IE. 🦸‍♀️🦸

https://www.facebook.com/share/p/19f2U3otAB/

CC: Lester Jay Cube and Merryrose Peros
